OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and windy day with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain at times. Rain most
OL,7,Flikely in the west with areas towards
OL,8,Feastern coasts staying dry with some
OL,9,Fbright or sunny spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy through the evening
OL,12,Fand overnight with rain feeding in
OL,13,Ffrom the west. This will see rain
OL,14,Fmainly focused in the west with
OL,15,Feastern areas staying largely dry.
OL,16,FWinds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
