OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAnother cloudy and dull day
OL,6,Fwith outbreaks of rain and drizzle
OL,7,Fthroughout, which may be heavy and
OL,8,Fpersistent at times, particularly in
OL,9,Fthe west. Breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fand breezy Monday and Tuesday with
OL,13,Frain spreading east. Rain mainly in
OL,14,Fthe west with many eastern parts
OL,15,Fseeing largely dry conditions. Drier
OL,16,FWednesday with bright or sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
